headline: American Council on Germany Honors Nikesh Arora with the John J. McCloy Award in New York
summary: The American Council on Germany (ACG) has honored Nikesh Arora, Chairman and CEO of Palo Alto Networks (NASDAQ: PANW), with this year's John J. McCloy Award. The ACG celebrated Arora for his work in building digital resilience across the Atlantic in a new era of AI transformation.
